        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Pre-Apprenticeships To Hardhats Act or the PATH Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Labor to provide grants to eligible entities to develop pre-apprenticeship programs in the building and construction trades that serve underrepresented populations, including individuals from low income and rural census tracts.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
